<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.6">
<l>orukāliṟ caṅkorukā liṟcakkara muḷḷaṭipo ṟittamainta</l>
<l>virukāluṅ koṇṭaṅkaṅ keḻutiṉāṟpō lilacciṉai paṭanaṭantu</l>
<l>perukāniṉ ṟaviṉpaveḷ ḷattiṉmēṟ piṉṉaiyum peytupeytu</l>
<l>karukārkka ṭalvaṇṇaṉ kāmartātai taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Walking so that marks appear as if [he] drew here and there</l>
<l>with [his] two feet that became still [upon the earth],</l>
<l>having imprinted the soles of [his] feet with</l>
<l>the conch on one foot [and] the discus on the other foot,</l>
<l>[he] pours down before and behind [himself]</l>
<l>a flood of delight that continuously spreads,</l>
<l>will the father of Kāma,</l> 
<l rend="indent">he with the complexion of the dark black ocean,</l>
<l>come with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
